comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was overturned and Miami is given possession.
LO SLA shows that Beal (WAS) makes contact with Dragic's (MIA) head on the shot attempt.
Gortat (WAS) sets the screen on Johnson (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Johnson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Wall (WAS) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Morris (WAS) makes marginal contact with Dragic (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Gortat (WAS) slides into Richardson (MIA) and affects his movement through the screen.
Morris (WAS) commits a take foul on Johnson (MIA).
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Whiteside (MIA).
